[size=12pt]100% barrows i cant really remember whats all on this one but its the one i posted a long time ago some of these photos may be outdated jad is 100% has a control panel Has tons of commands basic and others including ::lottery which wasn't all that bad to make. i now use a new and really nice updated server to this with a lot of the problems fixed if i get 50k plus dls ill post it.[/size] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/drop5.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/drop9.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/drop8.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/12.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/11.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/10.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/9.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/8.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/7.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/5.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/2.jpg[/img] [img]http://i879.photobucket.com/albums/ab352/awesome201212/1.jpg[/img]
after you acquire a clue scroll you need 2 things you clue scroll [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/eash0z.jpg[/img] and a shovel.[img]http://i50.tinypic.com/szhh88.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open at exact spot at slayer tower open it here. [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/2ms3p1f.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open at exact spot at dagg layer.[img]http://i46.tinypic.com/2cponrr.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open this at the exact spot near a cow open it here [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/dbigwk.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open this at home by some statues open it here [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/30t2s5z.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open this by some sand open it here [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/4hweu8.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open this between some arms in the museum open it here [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/av3l3c.jpg[/img]
If the clue scroll reads open this exactly spot in the bar [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/157174l.jpg[/img]
and you'll end up with a casket [img]http://i49.tinypic.com/22c313.jpg[/img]
[b][size=18pt]Thieving[/size][/b]
Start off by clicking HOME TELEPORT or type ::home.
Run south till you get to the square and go east till you get to the wall.
Then start off with the silk stall you get 50k every time. [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/65cnyu.jpg[/img]
Then when you get to level 50 move to either the:
cake stall where you get 30k every time but less exp [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/2aflhcp.jpg[/img]
silver stall where you get 100k every time [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/2ykgx00.jpg[/img]
or the spice stall where you get 10k every time [img]http://i45.tinypic.com/52b5gx.jpg[/img]
When your level 60 move to the vegetable stall where you get 150k every time [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/2ladb2g.jpg[/img]
Then when you are level 80 move to the gem stall where you get 500k each time [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/r1ydzc.jpg[/img]
When you hit level 90 move to the tea stall aka "1 million stall" where you get of course 1 mill every time [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/xm8kdv.jpg[/img]
Do this till you get level 99 and HOORAY YOU GET THE 99 THIEVING SKILL CAPE AND HOOD!!!!! [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/30bd4c1.jpg[/img]
Credits: Blurr for the base server and client 20% coders one and zero 75% pics from toy 5%
